;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">34. Carmo CN, Hacon S, Longo KM, Freitas S, Ignotti E, Ponce de Leon A, Artaxo P. Associa&ccedil;&atilde;o entre material particulado de queimadas e doen&ccedil;as respirat&oacute;rias na regi&atilde;o sul da Amaz&ocirc;nia brasileira. <em>Rev Panam Salud Publica</em> 2010;27(1):10-16. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">35. Rodrigues PCO, Ignotti E; Rosa AM; Hacon SS. Spatial distribution of asthma-related hospitalizations of the elderly in the Brazilian Amazon. <em>Rev Bras Epidemiol</em> 2010;13(3):1-10. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">36. Silva AMC. <em>Quantifica&ccedil;&atilde;o dos efeitos na sa&uacute;de da exposi&ccedil;&atilde;o &agrave; queima de biomassa: uma contribui&ccedil;&atilde;o ao entendimento dos efeitos da exposi&ccedil;&atilde;o ao material particulado (PM</em><sub><em>2,5</em></sub><em>) em grupos populacionais sens&iacute;veis na Amaz&ocirc;nia Legal</em> [tese]. Fiocruz: Rio de Janeiro; 2010. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">37. Andrade VSF. <em>Estudo da associa&ccedil;&atilde;o entre material particulado emitido em queimadas e doen&ccedil;as respirat&oacute;rias no munic&iacute;pio de Manaus, AM</em> [disserta&ccedil;&atilde;o]. INPA: Manaus; 2011</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">38. Oliveira BFA. <em>Avalia&ccedil;&atilde;o do risco a sa&uacute;de infantil relativa &agrave; exposi&ccedil;&atilde;o ao PM</em><sub><em>2,5</em></sub><em> proveniente da queima de biomassa no munic&iacute;pio de Tangar&aacute; da Serra - MT</em>. 2011 [disserta&ccedil;&atilde;o]. Fiocruz: Rio de Janeiro; 2010. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">39. Saldanha CT, Botelho C. Queimadas e suas influ&ecirc;ncias em crian&ccedil;as asm&aacute;ticas menores de cinco anos atendidas em um hospital p&uacute;blico. <em>Rev. bras. alerg. imunopatol.</em> 2008;31(3):108-112. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">40. Minist&eacute;rio da Sa&uacute;de. Secretaria de Vigil&acirc;ncia &agrave; Sa&uacute;de. <em>Vigil&acirc;ncia em sa&uacute;de ambiental relacionada &agrave; qualidade do ar - VIGIAR</em>. Bras&iacute;lia: MS; 2006. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">41. Organiza&ccedil;&atilde;o das Na&ccedil;&otilde;es Unidas para a Educa&ccedil;&atilde;o, a Ci&ecirc;ncia e a Cultura (Unesco). <em>Documento T&eacute;cnico contendo proposta de metodologia para implanta&ccedil;&atilde;o de unidades sentinelas para a vigil&acirc;ncia em sa&uacute;de ambiental relacionada &agrave; qualidade do ar</em>. Bras&iacute;lia: Unesco; 2006. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">Artigo apresentado em 01/04/2012 <br />Aprovado em 19/04/2012 <br />Vers&atilde;o final apresentada em 04/05/2012 </span></p>\r\n</article>','2021-09-29 15:30:26','2021-09-30 00:07:54',1),(8,'fogo perigo','fogo-perigo','<div id=\"main-content\" class=\"mh-content\" role=\"main\"><nav class=\"mh-breadcrumb\"><a href=\"https://ambientes.ambientebrasil.com.br\">In&iacute;cio</a><a href=\"https://ambientes.ambientebrasil.com.br/categoria/florestal\">Florestal</a><a href=\"https://ambientes.ambientebrasil.com.br/categoria/florestal/artigos\">Artigos</a>Queimadas, Inc&ecirc;ndios Florestais</nav>\r\n<article id=\"post-1826\" class=\"post-1826 post type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail hentry category-artigos tag-artigo tag-queimada\"><header class=\"entry-header clearfix\">\r\n<h1 class=\"entry-title\">Queimadas, Inc&ecirc;ndios Florestais</h1>\r\n</header>\r\n<div class=\"entry-content clearfix\">\r\n<div class=\"mh-social-top\">\r\n<div class=\"mh-share-buttons clearfix\"><a class=\"mh-facebook\" title=\"Compartilhar no Facebook\" href=\"https://ambientes.ambientebrasil.com.br/florestal/artigos/queimadas_incendios_florestais.html\"> </a> <a class=\"mh-twitter\" title=\"Tweetar esse artigo\" href=\"https://ambientes.ambientebrasil.com.br/florestal/artigos/queimadas_incendios_florestais.html\"> </a> <a class=\"mh-linkedin\" title=\"Compartilhar no Linkedin\" href=\"https://ambientes.ambientebrasil.com.br/florestal/artigos/queimadas_incendios_florestais.html\"> </a> <a class=\"mh-pinterest\" title=\"Compartilhar no Pinterest\" href=\"https://ambientes.ambientebrasil.com.br/florestal/artigos/queimadas_incendios_florestais.html\"> </a> <a class=\"mh-email\" title=\"Enviar este artigo para um amigo\" href=\"mailto:?subject=Queimadas%2C%20Inc%C3%AAndios%20Florestais&amp;body=https%3A%2F%2Fambientes.ambientebrasil.com.br%2Fflorestal%2Fartigos%2Fqueimadas_incendios_florestais.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"> </a> <a class=\"mh-print\" title=\"Imprimir este artigo\"> </a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://ambientes.ambientebrasil.com.br/florestal/artigos/midia/imagens/1242.jpg\" alt=\"q\" /></figure>\r\n<p>Segundo dados do INPE (Instituto Nacional de Pesquisas Espaciais), durante o per&iacute;odo de junho a novembro, grande parte do pa&iacute;s &eacute; acometido por queimadas, que se estendem praticamente por todas as regi&otilde;es, com maior ou menor intensidade. O fogo &eacute; normalmente empregado para fins diversos na agropecu&aacute;ria, na renova&ccedil;&atilde;o de &aacute;reas de pastagem, na remo&ccedil;&atilde;o de material acumulado, no preparo do corte manual em planta&ccedil;&otilde;es de cana-de-a&ccedil;&uacute;car etc. Trata-se de uma alternativa geralmente eficiente, r&aacute;pida e de custo relativamente baixo quando comparada a outras t&eacute;cnicas que podem ser utilizadas para o mesmo fim. Os Estados que, tradicionalmente, apresentam maior n&uacute;mero de focos de calor s&atilde;o Mato Grosso e Par&aacute;.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Focos de Calor</strong></p>\r\n<p>As queimadas s&atilde;o praticadas na prepara&ccedil;&atilde;o do solo para a agricultura, e a seca s&atilde;o as principais causas do alastramento do fogo nas matas do pa&iacute;s. Nas tabelas abaixo segue a evolu&ccedil;&atilde;o dos focos de inc&ecirc;ndio:</p>\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table\">\r\n<table>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Paran&aacute;</strong></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Meses</strong></td>\r\n<td><strong>&nbsp;2000&nbsp;</strong></td>\r\n<td><strong>&nbsp;2001&nbsp;</strong></td>\r\n<td><strong>&nbsp;2002&nbsp;</strong></td>\r\n<td><strong>&nbsp;2003&nbsp;</strong></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Janeiro</td>\r\n<td>34</td>\r\n<td>&ndash;</td>\r\n<td>47</td>\r\n<td>43</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Fevereiro</td>\r\n<td>9</td>\r\n<td>&ndash;</td>\r\n<td>24</td>\r\n<td>23</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Mar&ccedil;o</td>\r\n<td>&ndash;</td>\r\n<td>&ndash;</td>\r\n<td>19</td>\r\n<td>34</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Abril</td>\r\n<td>&ndash;</td>\r\n<td>44</td>\r\n<td>94</td>\r\n<td>80</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Maio</td>\r\n<td>&ndash;</td>\r\n<td>33</td>\r\n<td>65</td>\r\n<td>143</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Junho</td>\r\n<td>&ndash;</td>\r\n<td>54</td>\r\n<td>115</td>\r\n<td>157</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Julho</td>\r\n<td>&ndash;</td>\r\n<td>137</td>\r\n<td>96</td>\r\n<td>193</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Agosto</strong></td>\r\n<td><strong>926</strong></td>\r\n<td><strong>370</strong></td>\r\n<td>547</td>\r\n<td>501</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Setembro</strong></td>\r\n<td>407</td>\r\n<td>113</td>\r\n<td><strong>565</strong></td>\r\n<td><strong>&nbsp;1.446</strong>&nbsp;</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Outubro</td>\r\n<td>18</td>\r\n<td>&ndash;</td>\r\n<td>237</td>\r\n<td>692</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Novembro</td>\r\n<td>92</td>\r\n<td>&ndash;</td>\r\n<td>151</td>\r\n<td>351</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Dezembro</td>\r\n<td>170</td>\r\n<td>&ndash;</td>\r\n<td>127</td>\r\n<td>140</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>&nbsp;<strong>Total (m&eacute;dia)&nbsp;</strong></td>\r\n<td><strong>&nbsp;1.656&nbsp;</strong></td>\r\n<td><strong>751</strong></td>\r\n<td><strong>&nbsp;2.087&nbsp;</strong></td>\r\n<td><strong>&nbsp;3.803&nbsp;</strong></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</figure>\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table\">\r\n<table>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Brasil</strong></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Meses</strong></td>\r\n<td><strong>&nbsp;1997</strong></td>\r\n<td><strong>1998</strong></td>\r\n<td><strong>1999</strong></td>\r\n<td><strong>2000</strong></td>\r\n<td><strong>2001</strong></td>\r\n<td><strong>2002</strong></td>\r\n<td><strong>2003</strong></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Janeiro</td>\r\n<td>&ndash;</td>\r\n<td>&ndash;</td>\r\n<td>1.670</td>\r\n<td>1.997</td>\r\n<td>560</td>\r\n<td>1.654</td>\r\n<td>3.603</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Fevereiro</td>\r\n<td>&ndash;</td>\r\n<td>&ndash;</td>\r\n<td>9.359</td>\r\n<td>2.666</td>\r\n<td>1.139</td>\r\n<td>1.570</td>\r\n<td>2.367</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Mar&ccedil;o</td>\r\n<td>&ndash;</td>\r\n<td>&ndash;</td>\r\n<td>780</td>\r\n<td>850</td>\r\n<td>1.510</td>\r\n<td>1.679</td>\r\n<td>3.181</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Abril</td>\r\n<td>&ndash;</td>\r\n<td>&ndash;</td>\r\n<td>565</td>\r\n<td>431</td>\r\n<td>1.112</td>\r\n<td>1.682</td>\r\n<td>1.902</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Maio</td>\r\n<td>&ndash;</td>\r\n<td>1.081</td>\r\n<td>1.215</td>\r\n<td>2.273</td>\r\n<td>2.112</td>\r\n<td>3.818</td>\r\n<td>3.871</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Junho</td>\r\n<td>814</td>\r\n<td>2.914</td>\r\n<td>2.562</td>\r\n<td>6.316</td>\r\n<td>8.461</td>\r\n<td>10.840</td>\r\n<td>10.549</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Julho</td>\r\n<td>3.629</td>\r\n<td>7.198</td>\r\n<td>5.841</td>\r\n<td>4.933</td>\r\n<td>6.762</td>\r\n<td>10.770</td>\r\n<td>19.398</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Agosto</strong></td>\r\n<td><strong>17.257</strong></td>\r\n<td><strong>32.112</strong></td>\r\n<td><strong>32.170</strong></td>\r\n<td><strong>24.234</strong></td>\r\n<td><strong>32.911</strong></td>\r\n<td>47.266</td>\r\n<td>27.681</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Setembro</strong></td>\r\n<td>20.580</td>\r\n<td>33.613</td>\r\n<td>31.936</td>\r\n<td>24.775</td>\r\n<td>3.713</td>\r\n<td><strong>61.012</strong></td>\r\n<td><strong>57.262</strong></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Outubro</td>\r\n<td>14.188</td>\r\n<td>18.638</td>\r\n<td>24.153</td>\r\n<td>27.102</td>\r\n<td>&ndash;</td>\r\n<td>52.077</td>\r\n<td>43.058</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Novembro</td>\r\n<td>4.053</td>\r\n<td>5.823</td>\r\n<td>9.753</td>\r\n<td>8.496</td>\r\n<td>&ndash;</td>\r\n<td>30.356</td>\r\n<td>23.010</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Dezembro</td>\r\n<td>&ndash;</td>\r\n<td>3.911</td>\r\n<td>5.963</td>\r\n<td>4.645</td>\r\n<td>&ndash;</td>\r\n<td>11.649</td>\r\n<td>15.061</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>&nbsp;<strong>Total (m&eacute;dia)&nbsp;</strong></td>\r\n<td><strong>&nbsp;60.521&nbsp;</strong></td>\r\n<td><strong>&nbsp;105.290&nbsp;</strong></td>\r\n<td><strong>&nbsp;125.967&nbsp;</strong></td>\r\n<td><strong>&nbsp;108.718&nbsp;</strong></td>\r\n<td><strong>&nbsp;58.280&nbsp;</strong></td>\r\n<td><strong>&nbsp;243.373&nbsp;</strong></td>\r\n<td><strong>&nbsp;210.943&nbsp;</strong></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</figure>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: xx-small;\">obs.: (-) dados indispon&iacute;veis.&nbsp;Fonte das tabelas: Inpe &ndash; Instituro de Pesquisas Espaciais.</span></p>\r\n<p><strong>Diferen&ccedil;as entre focos de calor, inc&ecirc;ndio e queimadas:</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>Focos de calor</strong>: Qualquer temperatura registrada acima de 47&ordm;C. Um foco de calor n&atilde;o &eacute; necessariamente um foco de fogo ou inc&ecirc;ndio.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</article>\r\n</div>','2021-09-29 15:31:54','2021-09-29 15:31:54',3),(9,'Docker','Docker','<h1>algum artigo sobre docker</h1>','2021-09-29 20:43:41','2021-09-29 20:43:41',2),(10,'undefined','undefined','<p>Undefined = verifica se campo esta vazio</p>','2021-09-29 20:44:19','2021-09-29 20:44:19',2),(11,'IF {DINHEIRO}ELSE{NUMEROS}','IF-DINHEIROELSENUMEROS','<h1>ARTIGO DINHEIRO E REAL OU SO NUMEROS ??</h1>','2021-09-29 20:45:48','2021-09-29 20:45:48',1),(12,'Momentos','Momentos','<p>esta aqui seu momento</p>','2021-09-30 00:42:04','2021-09-30 00:42:04',5),(13,'amigo legal','amigo-legal','<p>sei la oque escrever</p>','2021-09-30 00:42:26','2021-09-30 00:42:26',5),(14,'mysql server','mysql-server','<p>????????????????????wwww</p>','2021-09-30 00:42:45','2021-09-30 00:42:45',1),(15,'debug.log','debug.log','<p>logs</p>','2021-09-30 00:43:10','2021-09-30 00:43:10',4),(16,'hohoho','hohoho','<p>hahaha</p>','2021-09-30 00:43:31','2021-09-30 00:43:31',1),(17,'estevesss','estevesss','<p>ola mund</p>','2021-09-30 00:43:47','2021-09-30 00:43:47',1),(18,'bkg-bkg','bkg-bkg','<p>bkgggg</p>','2021-09-30 00:44:05','2021-09-30 00:44:05',1);
